### Health checks
GET http://localhost:8000/health
GET http://localhost:8001/health
GET http://localhost:8002/health
GET http://localhost:8003/health
GET http://localhost:8004/health

### Create ride
POST http://localhost:8000/demo/request-ride
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passenger_id": 100,
  "from_zone": "A",
  "to_zone": "B"
}

### Accept ride
PATCH http://localhost:8000/demo/rides/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

### Start ride
PATCH http://localhost:8000/demo/rides/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "STARTED"
}

### Complete ride
PATCH http://localhost:8000/demo/rides/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}

### Read final view
GET http://localhost:8000/demo/rides/1
